title: U.N. adds site near Palestinian city of Jericho to World Heritage List
description: The vote to add the prehistoric site, Tell es-Sultan, took place at a meeting of UNESCO’s World Heritage Committee in the Saudi capital, Riyadh.

title: Villagers survived Morocco’s earthquake but lost nearly everything else
description: Life in Tiniskt was simple and good, residents said, even if it wasn’t easy. When the earthquake struck, this mountain village was decimated in a matter of seconds.

title: Ukraine live briefing: Kim Jong Un views Russian weaponry; Zelensky expected in Washington
description: The North Korean leader met Russian Defense Minister Sergei Shoigu in Vladivostok. Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky is set to visit Washington this week.

title: Ukrainian oligarch Ihor Kolomoisky under pressure in criminal cases
description: The former Dnipropetrovsk governor, once one of Ukraine’s most flamboyant billionaires, has been accused of stealing assets from PrivatBank, which he owned.
